                        "content": "<a href=\"http://www.newsnrn.com/wp-content/uploads/nepal-v-jersi.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-18419\" src=\"http://www.newsnrn.com/wp-content/uploads/nepal-v-jersi.png\" alt=\"nepal v jersi\" width=\"376\" height=\"72\" /></a>\r\n\r\nट्वान्टी ट्वान्टी विश्वकप छनोट चरणबाट लगभग बाहिरिसकेको नेपालले आफ्नो अन्तिम खेलमा जर्सीको सामना गर्दैछ | नेपाल टस हारेर पहिले ब्याटिंग गर्दैछ |\r\n\r\n<a title=\"http://www.starsports.com/cricket/tour/icc-world-t20-qualifier-2015-254/matchvideos/vod/video=icc-world-t20-qualifiers-nepal-jersey-match-free/index.html?__utma=231891677.826264869.1436451676.1437207424.1437209774.12&amp;__utmb=231891677.1.10.1437209774&amp;__utmc=231891677&amp;__utmx=-&amp;__utmz=231891677.1436451676.1.1.utmcsr=(direct)|utmccn=(direct)|utmcmd=(none)&amp;__utmv=-&amp;__utmk=42964454\" href=\"http://www.starsports.com/cricket/tour/icc-world-t20-qualifier-2015-254/matchvideos/vod/video=icc-world-t20-qualifiers-nepal-jersey-match-free/index.html?__utma=231891677.826264869.1436451676.1437207424.1437209774.12&amp;__utmb=231891677.1.10.1437209774&amp;__utmc=231891677&amp;__utmx=-&amp;__utmz=231891677.1436451676.1.1.utmcsr=(direct)|utmccn=(direct)|utmcmd=(none)&amp;__utmv=-&amp;__utmk=42964454\">लाइभ हेर्न यो लिंकमा जानुहोला </a>",
